THEORETICAL FOUNDATION

This project is inspired by Shikigaku Theory (識学理論), a management and
organizational design philosophy developed by Shikigaku Inc.

The implementation of hierarchical agent systems and responsibility allocation
draws inspiration from these principles, though this software is an independent
work and not affiliated with or endorsed by Shikigaku Inc.

